quran[10{c,v,t}:
39,22,bhala jis shakhs ka seenah khuda ne islam ke liye khol diya ho aur woh apne perwar-digaar ki taraf se roshni par ho ( tokiya woh sakht dil kafir ki terhan ho sakta hai ) pas un par afsos hai jin ke dil khuda ki yaad se sakht ho rahay hain. aur yahi log Sarih gumraahi mein hain
39,23,khuda ne nihayat achi baatein nazil farmai hain ( yani ) kitaab ( jis ki ayatain baahum ) millti jalti ( hain ) aur duhrai jati ( hain ) jo log apne perwar-digaar se drtay hain un ke badan ke ( is se ) rongte kharray ho jatay hain. phir un ke badan aur dil naram ( ho kar ) khuda ki yaad ki taraf ( mutwajjah ) ho jatay hain. yahi khuda ki hadaayat hai woh is se jis ko chahta hai hadaayat deta hai. aur jis ko khuda gumraah kere is ko koi hadaayat dainay wala nahi
39,24,bhala jo shakhs qayamat ke din apne munh se buray azaab ko rokta ho (kiya woh waisa ho sakta hai jo chain mein ho ) aur zaalmon se kaha jaye ga ke jo kuch tum karte rahay they is ke mazay chako
39,25,jo log un se pehlay they unhon ne bhi takzieeb ki thi to un par azaab aisi jagah se agaya ke un ko khabar hi nah thi
39,26,phir un ko khuda ne duniya ki zindagi mein ruswai ka maza chakkha diya. aur akhirat ka azaab to bohat bara hai. kash yeh samajh rakhtay
39,27,aur hum ne logon ke ( samjhane ke ) liye is quran mein har terhan ki misalein bayan ki hain taakay woh nasiyaat pakren
39,28,yeh ) quran arabi ( hai ) jis mein koi aib ( aur ikhtilaaf ) nahi taakay woh dar manen
39,29,khuda aik misaal bayan karta hai ke 1 shakhs hai jis mein kayi ( aadmi ) shareek hain. ( mukhtalif ul mizaj aur ) badkhu aur aik aadmi khaas aik shakhs ka ( ghulam ) hai. bhala dono ki haalat barabar hai. ( nahi ) ا Alhamdu lillaa balkay yeh aksar log nahi jantay
39,30,( ae paighambar ) tum bhi mar jao ge aur yeh bhi mar jayen ge
39,31,phir tum sab qayamat ke din apne perwar-digaar ke samnay chugro ge ( aur jhagra Faisal kardiya jaye ga )
